Class StrongComponentClusterer<V,E>

java.lang.Object
net.sf.opendse.visualization.algorithm.StrongComponentClusterer<V,E>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of vertices
E - the type of edges
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.commons.collections15.Transformer<Graph<V,E>,Set<Set<V>>>
public class StrongComponentClusterer<V,E> extends Object implements org.apache.commons.collections15.Transformer<Graph<V,E>,Set<Set<V>>>
The StrongComponentClusterer clusters a graph into strongly connected components using Tarjan's algorithms. See: Robert Tarjan: Depth-first search and linear graph algorithms. In: SIAM Journal on Computing. Vol. 1 (1972), No. 2, P. 146-160.
